{"tid":1322994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［不喜勿進］我信有白警！","createTime":"2019-07-16T06:05:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:39:35.000Z","uid":148322,"like":17,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"cf6a749bf67bf37e9dd489736e69dbff960ce9ee","tid":1322994,"uid":148322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"雨傘果時我信有白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魚蛋果陣我信仲有小小白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到今次修改612之後，乜Q有白警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身不由己既藉口，食屎啦黑狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲想自慰心態覺得錯不在自己，出手趕人入站係你，趕曬啲人入去封站又係你封既，唔洗係覺醒既市民面前扮可憐呀！<br />\n<br />\n你地班黑狗唔好死左同傷左，番工果刻就已經浪費緊我地既汗血錢喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要幫住暴政既，無一個係無辜既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33aa3de0853817b29abc7f6f1ff53da608d54f7","tid":1322994,"uid":277650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"他們只是「鎗」，上位者善良，它們就是「善良的鎗」，反之... <br />\n與前線人員溝通亦是沒有效果的。亦無需攻訐、謾罵，反而制做機會給對方。而且被調派至前線的都不會是會有可能同情市民的，要爭取就爭取其他敢怒不敢言的人，讓他們在內部協助，發揮影響力。"},{"pid":"c8e6e4d2f6541b2ddc66d9c00f1a9195e006d444","tid":1322994,"uid":1425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:09:31.000Z","msg":"白警=白人警察=逃輝"},{"pid":"c36fbfc8df293dd5ac08f76e6a00622011c5cc6c","tid":1322994,"uid":224429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"有都唔關我地事<br />\n我地唔想知"},{"pid":"118babad1b5dacc3ae469ed86df527c4665aa89d","tid":1322994,"uid":148322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e33aa3de0853817b29abc7f6f1ff53da608d54f7","tid":1322994,"uid":277650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"他們只是「鎗」，上位者善良，它們就是「善良的鎗」，反之... <br />\n與前線人員溝通亦是沒有效果的。亦無需攻訐、謾罵，反而制做機會給對方。而且被調派至前線的都不會是會有可能同情市民的，要爭取就爭取其他敢怒不敢言的人，讓他們在內部協助，發揮影響力。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"你咁講佢地只係一個工具 冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以連埋佢地啲家屬都唔洗以人來看待佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d9223096a2c60c7f7d98bca70655065691ac62","tid":1322994,"uid":181097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"72bbdf8e366ba21e2561c67662347384f90fbe2f","tid":1322994,"uid":277650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"118babad1b5dacc3ae469ed86df527c4665aa89d","tid":1322994,"uid":148322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e33aa3de0853817b29abc7f6f1ff53da608d54f7","tid":1322994,"uid":277650,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:08:14.000Z","msg":"他們只是「鎗」，上位者善良，它們就是「善良的鎗」，反之... <br />\n與前線人員溝通亦是沒有效果的。亦無需攻訐、謾罵，反而制做機會給對方。而且被調派至前線的都不會是會有可能同情市民的，要爭取就爭取其他敢怒不敢言的人，讓他們在內部協助，發揮影響力。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:09:55.000Z","msg":"你咁講佢地只係一個工具 冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以連埋佢地啲家屬都唔洗以人來看待佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:20:05.000Z","msg":"家屬還家屬，罪不及妻孥，無謂放大。"},{"pid":"877c8d758c52f762dafb3d279c742bea71f87ab4","tid":1322994,"uid":277650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c36fbfc8df293dd5ac08f76e6a00622011c5cc6c","tid":1322994,"uid":224429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:09:51.000Z","msg":"有都唔關我地事<br />\n我地唔想知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"無謂與全天下為敵，可用就用"},{"pid":"cd38fef55b5c8106055af7cc99a2151c1ee09780","tid":1322994,"uid":277650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11d9223096a2c60c7f7d98bca70655065691ac62","tid":1322994,"uid":181097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"既為廢物